UI/UX DESIGN & FRONTEND WEB DEVELOPMENT

TaskClear | LA Hacks 2023

overview.

Time blocking, a trending time management method, divides the day into task-specific blocks. Yet, students often hesitate due to uncertain task durations, and tracking times can be bothersome. The app tackles this by furnishing analytics, presenting users with their average study time per course, simplifying time blocking.
